OL,3,CGrassroots football games postponed in
OL,4,CCardiff as referees strike over
OL,5,Cviolence
OL,7,FGrassroots football games in Cardiff
OL,8,Fhave been called off this weekend as
OL,9,Freferees have withdrawn their labour
OL,10,Fover violence and abuse.
OL,12,FThe strike is affecting the Cardiff
OL,13,Fand District League's adult fixtures,
OL,14,FCardiff Combination League, and
OL,15,FLazarou Cardiff Sunday League.
OL,17,FCardiff Referees Society say their
OL,18,Fmembers "are concerned about the
OL,19,Fincreased number of match abandonments
OL,20,Fand most recently the assault of a
OL,21,Freferee."
