OL,3,CGrassroots football games postponed in
OL,4,CCardiff as referees strike over
OL,5,Cviolence
OL,7,FSouth Wales Police confirmed they are
OL,8,F"investigating an assault on a 49-year-
OL,9,Fold man from Barry. The assault took
OL,10,Fplace on Sunday October 27 at around
OL,11,F1:00pm at a football match in
OL,12,FSt.Mellons."
OL,14,FIn a statement the CRS said "the
OL,15,Fdeteriorating behaviour on and off the
OL,16,Fpitch cannot continue.
OL,18,F"It is hoped that this unprecedented
OL,19,Faction will help send a clear message."
