OL,3,CGrassroots football games postponed in
OL,4,CCardiff as referees strike over
OL,5,Cviolence
OL,7,FSouth Wales FA say they condemn all
OL,8,Facts of violence on the football pitch
OL,9,Fand continue to strive to support
OL,10,Fofficials and deal with offences as
OL,11,Fthey occur.
OL,13,FBoth Cardiff Combination League and
OL,14,Fthe Lazarou league have publicly
OL,15,Fstated their support for the strike
OL,16,Fand have taken steps to postpone all
OL,17,Ffixtures.
